title: 插件导致蹦服原因
author: Mew_Ming
txt_content:
com.comphenix.protocol.compat.netty.independent.NettyChannelInjector.processSending(NettyChannelInjector.java:417) [ProtocolLib.jar:?]

replies.author: pzhYelanG
replies.txt_content: 你把你觉得可疑的插件删了试试，应该是某个插件和这个插件冲突了
